#. translators: %s: location of the API key inside the RedaQuest app, already
#. wrapped in <strong>.
#: redaquest-connector.php:1136
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Tip: connecting above sets this up automatically. To configure sync manually"
" instead, get your API key in the RedaQuest app under %s."
msgstr ""
"Tipp: Das Verbinden oben richtet dies automatisch ein. Wenn du die "
"Synchronisierung stattdessen manuell einrichten möchtest, findest du deinen "
"API-Schlüssel in der RedaQuest-App unter %s."

#: src/index.js:573
